{"tid":1632111,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人，唔好放棄呀！","createTime":"2019-10-06T17:00:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T17:12:23.000Z","uid":318271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"de843872deee7a301bc50496063b08c1be46c0b6","tid":1632111,"uid":318271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:00:58.000Z","msg":"雖然呢兩日有好多兩極化既聲音，<br />\n但我地要記住：兄弟爬山，各自努力。<br />\n記住核爆都唔割！<br />\n<br />\n香港人，唔好放棄，繼續勇往直前！<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可"},{"pid":"8bbaf8488241c39699d10eac225a7460270b130d","tid":1632111,"uid":318271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:01:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d9e562f43bda690e16c1f488224b923253b1435c","tid":1632111,"uid":318271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:01:22.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"f4f10d859d24e5ecf4657485d33dd3b81a2e86a6","tid":1632111,"uid":318271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:01:34.000Z","msg":"再再推"},{"pid":"76ee37be50648177f7ef2d6d536359c072d16868","tid":1632111,"uid":318271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:01:45.000Z","msg":"再再再推"},{"pid":"d886acf9cf0c9a76091adf9bfbd787c1d8546581","tid":1632111,"uid":318271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:02:01.000Z","msg":"再再再再推"},{"pid":"39c860e0750c5f40cef391894da99d8aceaf73e9","tid":1632111,"uid":318271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:02:19.000Z","msg":"再再再再再推"},{"pid":"6b6533d0d15474ef791baff83c8ed030fc81035e","tid":1632111,"uid":318271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:02:39.000Z","msg":"再再再再再再推"},{"pid":"b8858213f106a7542fc91db957faa7a9657223b1","tid":1632111,"uid":287211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:03:03.000Z","msg":"越亂 証明林鄭越有用去平亂<br />\n<br />\n越亂就想美國唔好企我們呢到 影響法案辣度<br />\n<br />\n我們拉長嚟玩 條臭西趁越亂 乘機出師有名推其他法<br />\n<br />\n冚家產 蒙面法之後 佢點到會贏<br />\n<br />\n1） 更亂 可推其他乜撚緊急法 96小時乜春之類法<br />\n<br />\n2） 平靜咗 証明條蒙面法係有用 回復少少秩序之類<br />\n<br />\n所以條臭西點都贏<br />\n<br />\n但我地冷靜下先 亂同平靜D的結果 邊個畫面達到制裁目標容易些？ 當然我假設大家想班狗賊同我們欖炒! 記得謝蛇移民case? 呢D先至係我哋要的清算目標！<br />\n<br />\n所以 忍一下先 唔好比條臭西帶到我哋！<br />\n<br />\n我不是叫大家晤搞 只是拉長嚟玩 有先後次序<br />\n<br />\n我哋翻新黨鐵計劃延遲二三星期 黨鐡仲會係到 所以押後一下！ 大家想想！"},{"pid":"f9bedd6d4fcbbd4804e69b36d7b028e75f11102d","tid":1632111,"uid":318271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:03:42.000Z","msg":"再再再再再再再推"},{"pid":"d71eb3dd86ab91ac8c9ceb04cea8e86fd4810c7f","tid":1632111,"uid":318271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:04:37.000Z","msg":"再再再再再再再再推"},{"pid":"3ba8261b8c891fe94f6b8bed15b9dcafefba7587","tid":1632111,"uid":318271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:05:02.000Z","msg":"再再再再再再再再再推"},{"pid":"9c01dc1db7508182c7f02f0889925de6f62d0dc1","tid":1632111,"uid":318271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:06:31.000Z","msg":"再再再再再再再再再再推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然我係p牌，但香港係我屋企，我唔想無左香港，<br />\n大家幫手推下"},{"pid":"0b48a569b8bc02014d4b261ac9796c93cfd7cbfb","tid":1632111,"uid":318271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:06:57.000Z","msg":"再再再再再再再再再再再推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然我係p牌，但香港係我屋企，我唔想無左香港，<br />\n大家幫手推下"},{"pid":"23c11869897d149855a081fffe84da80c9fdd479","tid":1632111,"uid":318271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:07:12.000Z","msg":"再再再再再再再再再再再再推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然我係p牌，但香港係我屋企，我唔想無左香港，<br />\n大家幫手推下"},{"pid":"531faa6846205f57981a073dfde414ffb6704d73","tid":1632111,"uid":318271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:07:35.000Z","msg":"再再再再再再再再再再再再再推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然我係p牌，但香港係我屋企，我唔想無左香港，<br />\n大家幫手推下"},{"pid":"d7626c5f08b4bc1e4724e71fc649474b2b2552b4","tid":1632111,"uid":318271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:07:47.000Z","msg":"再再再再再再再再再再再再再再推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\